Material and distribution. Holotype examined at the Zoölogisch Museum Amsterdam ( ZMA –
POR 11323
), collected at Jamaica , Discovery Bay, Long-Term Study Site (LTS), 83.8 m . The material reviewed here includes (but is not restricted to) specimens from the Bahamas (INV– POR 817 , INV– POR 935 ), Jamaica (INV– POR 1008 ), Belize (INV– POR 949 ), San Andres Island (INV– POR 979 ), Rosario Islands (INV– POR 971 ) and Santa Marta (INV– POR 871 ).

